.head 9 -  Set sMessageText = sMessageText || '

If any of the items above are not immediately available please notify sender via return mail.

Attached is a HIWG Flat File version of the Purchase order, you may wish to incorporate this into your system using the HIWG standards available for download at
www.hiwg.org.au.

'  || sSenderName || '
' || sSenderEmail
